title: Kenneth Cole Reaction Men's Watch Cases at Bed Bath & Beyond
description: Protect and keep your watches organized with this sophisticated storage box or watch winder case. Perfect gifts for graduation, Father's Day, birthdays, and more. Thanks for watching. Make sure to subscribe to the Bed Bath & Beyond YouTube Channel.
transcripts: Watch case with drawer hold sup to six watches. It has watch forms that help watch bands keep their shape. There is a glass window lid to display watches and keep them clean and protected. The lower drawer has multiple compartments to hold keys, cufflings, money clips, or keepsakes. The watch winder holds up to two watches. Electrically powered, it comes with an AC adapter and automatically winds kinetic watches. It has three different rotation modes and a glass window lid to keep watches clean and protected. The Hudson Watch Case ad Watch Winder by Kenneth Cole Reaction Home are available exclusively online and at select Bed Bath and Beyond stores. Make sure to view the other items available in the men's Hudson collection.
